name: Techno-Cultural Evolution
description: What does the future of NFT culture look like? As a protopian, it would be better if I don't speculate too much about the future but instead, look back at the progress of the past civilizations. My views on socio-cultural evolutions are about daily incremental progress, focusing on the here and now. The visual was done by @neroone__ , and ideate by me, @acesun07. I'm posting on behalf of NFXT Collective, and all the proceed will be donated to support the CC non-profit. #NFTsForAll #WorldArtDay
